entries.femaleVariant: Damn, those cosplayers wind me up. Tellin' everybody else how to live? Fuckin' freeloaders. And proud of it!
I mean – been where, huh? Done what, these dudes? No career, no kids, no nothin'!
Failed at everything you've tried? Oh yeah, don't sweat it, be a monk!
C'mon, cut 'em some slack. These guys do good, help people, some of 'em.
Fuck that! Cockrotten hypocrites, all of 'em. Talkin' shit about implants, any kind of tech's no good, but look around – whaddaya see?
I dunno, go ahead an' tell me.
Machines! Electrified, electronic machines in the temples themselves. Tellin' ya – hypocrites.
Choom, you got a lotta passion in you, conviction! Y'ever though of, uh, takin' vows, joinin' 'em?
